These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, mango, strawberry, watermelon
4 different pets are kept: hamster, rabbit, mouse, chinchilla
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, roller, motorbike, scooter
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the person driving the scooter is the owner of the hamster##1
3. the person eating strawberry is on the far left##1
4. the person eating lime is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is between the person driving the motorbike and the person eating mango##2
6. the person driving the roller is the owner of the mouse##1
7. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | strawberry | watermelon  | mango | lime  |
| Pet         | chinchilla    | rabbit  | hamster       | mouse     |
| Transport   | motorbike     | car | scooter       | roller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, dancing, photography, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, epic, thriller, disaster
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, rugby, skateboarding, rowing
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is between the person watching disaster movies and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
5. the person watching disaster movies is the person who's sport is rugby##1
6. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
7. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | dancing | baking    | woodworking  | photography |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster  | animation  | epic   | thriller    |
| Sport         | rugby | rowing | biathlon | skateboarding      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, coffee, iced-tea, juice
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, dancing, hiking, card-games
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, electronic, hip-hop, gospel
1. the fan of electronic is between the fan of gospel and the person drinking coffee##2
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the fan of soul##1
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left##1
6. the fan of soul is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
7. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | coffee | juice         | fanta   | iced-tea    |
| Hobby         | dancing | card-games | rock-climbing | hiking |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop   | electronic        | gospel      | soul   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, argentine, malaysian, brazilian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, handball, ice-hockey, badminton
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, subway, skateboard, bike
1. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is between the person driving the bike and the brazilian##2
3. the malaysian is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the malaysian is on the right of the nigerian##1
6. the person driving the bike is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person driving the subway##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Nationality   | brazilian        | argentine   | nigerian | malaysian |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | parkour | handball    | badminton |
| Transport     | skateboard       | motorbike     | bike       | subway    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, mirinda
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, reading, cooking, skydiving
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, rugby, baseball, sailing
1. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
2. the person who's sport is sailing is the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
7. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who's hobby is card-games##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | juice | mirinda      | hot-chocolate       | soy-milk   |
| Hobby      | card-games   | reading  | skydiving | cooking     |
| Sport      | rugby     | sailing | baseball        | biathlon |

