.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, nectarine, lemon, pumpkin
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, traveling, magic-tricks, reading
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, rugby, skiing, water-polo
1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
3. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
5. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's sport is skiing##2
6. the person eating nectarine is between the person eating pomegranate and the person eating lemon##2
7. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food    | lemon | nectarine  | pomegranate | pumpkin      |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks  | reading  | writing | traveling |
| Sport   | water-polo | cricket | rugby | skiing     |

