The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, satire, animation, family
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, rugby, water-polo, cricket
1. the person who's sport is cricket is the person watching satire movies##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person watching documentary movies##1
3. the person watching animation movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
5. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
6. the person eating grapefruit is between the person watching satire movies and the person watching animation movies##2
7. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Food          | blueberry  | grapefruit    | strawberry | lime  |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | family       | satire        | documentary    |
| Sport         | rugby | weightlifting | cricket  | water-polo |

