.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, singing, traveling, drawing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, scientific, thriller, adventure
4 different pets are kept: mouse, hedgehog, turtle, goldfish
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is between the owner of the goldfish and the person who's hobby is singing##2
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
4. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
5. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | drawing  | singing | traveling | fishing |
| Movie-Genre   | animation  | adventure | scientific   | thriller         |
| Pet           | mouse | turtle  | hedgehog   | goldfish      |

