1. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is the person eating pineapple##1
3. the owner of the horse is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the owner of the horse and the person eating pear##2
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the owner of the rabbit##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is the owner of the pony##1
7. the person who's hobby is cooking is the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
