3. the person drinking tea is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
6. the owner of the cat is on the far right##1
7. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | cola | hot-chocolate     | tea | lemonade       |
| Hobby      | baking  | magic-tricks | video-games  | dancing |
| Pet        | snake  | guinea-pig      | chinchilla        | cat      |

