.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-14::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, freelancer, nurse, engineer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, sports, spy, mystery
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, train, boat, snowmobile
1. the person watching epic movies is the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person driving the boat is the nurse##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the left of the doctor##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person driving the train is between the person watching spy movies and the nurse##2
6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the train is the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Job           | freelancer | engineer | nurse    | doctor   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy      | sports   | mystery | epic |
| Transport     | quad-bike     | train       | boat        | snowmobile    |

