.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, sudoku, collecting, singing
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, electrician, scientist, manager
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, ice-hockey, weightlifting, basketball
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
2. the person who's sport is basketball is the person who's hobby is singing##1
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is the manager##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the photographer and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
6. the scientist is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person who's sport is basketball and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |        2        |       3        |       4        |
| Hobby   | collecting   | sudoku           | dancing         | singing      |
| Job     | photographer | scientist | manager | electrician |
| Sport   | weightlifting     | ice-hockey         | snowboarding       | basketball        |

