.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, water, hot-chocolate, almond-milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, techno, d&b, metal
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, british, dutch, spanish
1. the fan of house is the person drinking water##1
2. the person drinking juice is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the british##2
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the fan of techno##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the fan of d&b and the spanish##2
5. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
6. the brazilian is between the dutch and the fan of metal##2
7. the fan of house is the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Beverage      | water | hot-chocolate | juice   | almond-milk |
| Music-Genre   | house  | techno    | d&b   | metal     |
| Nationality   | spanish  | dutch | brazilian | british   |

