.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, juice, cola, sprite
There 4 different types of food: mango, cabbage, pear, plum
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, surfing, lacrosse, climbing
1. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1
2. the person eating pear is between the person drinking sprite and the person who's sport is lacrosse##2
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far right##1
5. the person eating mango is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
6. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person eating pear##1
7. the person drinking cola is the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | milk    | juice | sprite           | cola |
| Food       | mango | pear    | cabbage          | plum   |
| Sport      | lacrosse  | surfing   | climbing | parkour  |

