4. the person drinking 7up is between the person watching musical movies and the person watching crime movies##2
5. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
6. the owner of the bird is between the person drinking coffee and the owner of the pony##2
7. the person watching spy movies is the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
