.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, broccoli, potato, peach
4 different pets are kept: snake, rat, pony, guinea-pig
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, bus, car, trike
1. the owner of the snake is on the far left##1
2. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
3. the person driving the bus is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
4. the person eating potato is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the trike is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
6. the owner of the rat is between the person eating peach and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | peach | broccoli | nectarine | potato |
| Pet         | snake       | rat     | pony   | guinea-pig   |
| Transport   | scooter | bus | car | trike |

 